Make Key be List with 1 and 2
Make Data be Map with Key meaning "pair" and "name" meaning "Ada"

Expect Use Map Has with Data and Key is true

Make Maybe Pair be Use Map Get with Data and Key as Maybe String
Match Maybe Pair
  When Some Pair
    Expect Pair is "pair"
  When nothing
    Expect false is true

Make Missing be Use Map Get with Data and "missing" as Maybe String
Match Missing
  When Some Value
    Expect false is true
  When nothing
    Expect true is true

Make Name be Use Map Get with Data and "missing" and Otherwise be "fallback"
Expect Name is "fallback"

Use Map Put with Data and "score" and 271
Expect Use Map Get with Data and "score" and Otherwise be 0 is 271

Make Keys be Use Map Keys with Data
Make Values be Use Map Values with Data
Make Entries be Use Map Entries with Data
Expect Length of Keys is 3
Expect Length of Values is 3
Expect Length of Entries is 3

Make Other be Map with "score" meaning 300 and "language" meaning "271"
Make Merged be Use Map Merge with Data and Other
Expect Use Map Get with Merged and "score" and Otherwise be 0 is 300
Expect Use Map Get with Data and "score" and Otherwise be 0 is 271

Use Map Remove with Data and "score"
Expect Use Map Has with Data and "score" is false
